{"000-section": {"000-title": "Punjab Sarbat Sehat Bima Yojana (SSBY) \u2013 Universal Health Insurance Scheme from July"}, "001-section": {"000-title": "Punjab govt. to start Sarbat Sehat Bima Yojana (SSBY) from 1 July 2019, universal health insurance scheme to cover 43.18 beneficiaries, people can avail free and cashless treatment upto Rs. 5 lakh at all govt. & 364 private hospitals"}, "002-section": {"000-title": "Punjab Sarbat Sehat Bima Yojana (SSBY) 2019", "001-normal": "The important features and highlights of Sarbat Sehat Bima Yojana in Punjab are as follows:-", "002-listElement": "- Universal Health Insurance Coverage of Rs. 5 lakh to all SSBY beneficiaries.", "003-listElement": "- Cashless treatment at all government hospitals along with 364 private empanelled hospitals.", "004-listElement": "- Claim settlement to be done at the hospital as this is not a reimbursement scheme rather a cashless treatment scheme.", "005-listElement": "- There is no limit on family size as all the family members would be eligible.", "006-listElement": "-  A total number of 43.18 lakh families in Punjab to be covered under SSBY Scheme in Punjab. These include:-", "007-listElement": "- The beneficiaries includes the 14.86 lakh families already covered under the [Pradhan Mantri Jan Arogya Yojana (PMJAY)](https://sarkariyojana.com/pradhan-mantri-jan-arogya-yojana-pmjay/) in Punjab.", "008-listElement": "- Around 20.48 lakh other poor families possessing blue cards.", "009-listElement": "- 7.84 lakh families from various departments like 5 lakh farmers under Punjab Mandi Board.", "010-listElement": "- 46,000 families under Excise and Taxation Department", "011-listElement": "- 2.38 lakh construction workers registered with construction worker\u2019s welfare board.", "012-normal": "The state govt. of Punjab has already prepared a database of 43.18 lakh beneficiary families. The Sarbat Sehat Bima Yojana is going to be implemented from 1 July 2019.", "013-normal": "The cost of premium for the families covered under the central govt\u2019s PMJAY scheme would be borne by the center and the Punjab govt. in 60:40 ratio.  \n **Also Read** \u2013 [Punjab Sarbat Sehat Bima Yojana E-Cards to Beneficiaries](https://sarkariyojana.com/punjab-sarbat-sehat-bima-yojana-e-cards-beneficiaries/)  \n **Also Read** \u2013 [Punjab Sarbat Sehat Bima Yojna List of Hospitals](https://sarkariyojana.com/sarbat-sehat-bima-yojana-hospital-list-punjab/)", "014-normal": "For the rest of 28.32 lakh families, the complete premium amount would be borne by the Punjab government.", "015-normal": "Source / Reference Link: https://www.business-standard.com/article/pti-stories/punjab-to-roll-out-universal-health-insurance-scheme-from-july-119061301073\\_1.html"}}